{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4cb8bd4298","title":"中共中央关于点名批判陈丕显曹荻秋问题的指示","origin":"1967年5月27日红代会清华井冈山一部第三动态组编《动态》第61期。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ee1b9b2c17","index":0,"year":1967,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"4cb8bd4298"}],"tags":[{"id":"2d13338754","name":"指示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"7b9fce9b32","name":"曹荻秋","type":"人物"},{"id":"e759231f2d","name":"农业战线","type":"主题/事件"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"f10c9d6647","name":"中共中央"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"d7fd99a67f","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于点名批判陈丕显曹荻秋问题的指示","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4cb8bd4298"},{"id":"da804d87c0","type":"authors","text":"中共中央","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4cb8bd4298"},{"id":"c830e3b90a","type":"subtitle","text":"陈曹的问题要害是以下几点：","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4cb8bd4298"},{"id":"f6a5ca9a97","type":"paragraph","text":"（1）五三年与高岗一起反对毛主席。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4cb8bd4298"},{"id":"5f533045ab","type":"paragraph","text":"（2）五五年与反革命分子潘汉年一起搞反革命活动。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4cb8bd4298"},{"id":"f608f791bd","type":"paragraph","text":"（3）五六年在市党代会上攻击柯庆施同志。","index":5,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4cb8bd4298"},{"id":"00ab9468b2","type":"paragraph","text":"（4）反对农业合作化运动。","index":6,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4cb8bd4298"},{"id":"7b3ea0b067","type":"paragraph","text":"（5）六五年把共产党员名单交给资方，向资产阶级投降。","index":7,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4cb8bd4298"},{"id":"077a5dfe5d","type":"paragraph","text":"（6）五七年反右派的问题，五九年借反右倾攻击柯老。","index":8,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4cb8bd4298"},{"id":"65a0b6b5f8","type":"paragraph","text":"（7）大刮资产阶级表扬风，为地、富、反、坏、右摆功。","index":9,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4cb8bd4298"},{"id":"49f184a4b7","type":"paragraph","text":"（8）攻击三面红旗。","index":10,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4cb8bd4298"},{"id":"6ccd49cadc","type":"paragraph","text":"（9）贯彻形“左”实右刘少奇“桃园”经验。","index":11,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4cb8bd4298"},{"id":"337819636b","type":"appellation","text":"","index":12,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4cb8bd4298"}],"page":{"id":"018b449b04","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"4cb8bd4298","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}